[+++ b/TESTING.asciidoc, +, +== Environment misc, +, +There is a known issue with macOS localhost resolve strategy that can cause, +some integration tests to fail. This is because integration tests have timings, +for cluster formation, discovery, etc. that can be exceeded if name resolution, +takes a long time., +To fix this, make sure you have your computer name (as returned by `hostname`), +inside `/etc/hosts`, e.g.:, +...., +127.0.0.1       localhost ElasticMBP.local, +255.255.255.255 broadcasthost, +::1             localhost ElasticMBP.local`, +....]